(h_n)
h_0 =1 , h_1 = 2, h_2 =3
h_n = h_{n-1} + h_{n-2} + h_{n-3}
n\ge 3
h_n\le 2^n
n\ge 0
2^{n-1}+2^{n-2}+2^{n-3}=2^n\cdot\left (\frac12+\frac14+\frac18\right)
n
n = 0
h_0 = 1 = 2^0
n < k
n = k+1
h_{k+1} = h_k + h_{k-1} + h_{k-2} \leq 2^k + 2^{k-1} + 2^{k-2} = \dfrac{2^{k+1}}{2} + \dfrac{2^{k+1}}{4} + \dfrac{2^{k+2}}{8} = \dfrac{7}{8} \cdot 2^{k+1} < 2^{k+1}
